---
title: Korean Style Honey Beef Noodles with Pepper, Lime and Peanuts
description: Ready in less than 25 minutes, these Speedy Korean Style Honey Beef Noodles combine spicy-sweet gochujang with honey to make a deliciously sticky sauce to coat the noodles and beef. Finish with lime juice and sprinkle with peanuts for full-on flavour.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R13_W22_UK_R17179-3_Main_low-c6eddef5.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/66c6124dd7b27e8034f6d5b1-en-GB.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipes/korean-style-honey-beef-noodles-66c6124dd7b27e8034f6d5b1
servings: 2
course: main course
time required: 20 minutes
author: HelloFresh
cuisine: Korean
